        &kp LSHFT   &trans     &kp SQT         &kp DOUBLE_QUOTES  &kp LBKT    &kp RBKT      &kp NUMBER_4  &kp NUMBER_5  &kp NUMBER_6  &kp KP_MINUS
&trans  &kp KP_NUM  &kp CAPS   &kp INSERT      &trans             &kp LPAR    &kp RPAR      &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &kp BSLH
                               &trans          &trans             &trans      &kp NUMBER_0  &mo 3         &trans
            >;
